CULP BROTHERS, a Copartnership Composed of Sherman Culp and Bert Culp, and Sherman Culp and Bert Culp as Individuals, v. B. N. BARNS. SAME v. Burr PORTER. Nos. 85, 86. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Aug. 2, 1929. Simms & Botts, of Albuquerque, N. M., for appellants. A. L. Zinn, of Gallup, N. M., and A. T. Hannett, of Albuquerque, N. M., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed August 2, 1929, on stipulation.
